# Living Foundations

> Living Foundations is a health, wellness, and mind-body-spirit content brand run by Karan Chandra Jugran (YouTube: @KaranJugran). Content covers practical fitness form/technique, breathing and pranayama, sleep, injury recovery, journaling, meditation, and psychology/self-improvement topics. Each article on this site is a written companion piece to a YouTube video, summarizing and explaining the video's actual content in English (source videos are in Hindi).

